{"tid":1500631,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"習主席是世上最偉大的皇帝","createTime":"2019-08-24T05:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T16:26:57.000Z","uid":213969,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"297ed48d362d84f977fa83ea6c9153d438558867","tid":1500631,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:39:13.000Z","msg":"習主席不但勤政愛民 憂國憂民 <br />\n豐功偉業更早已遠超始皇高袓、太宗太祖<br />\n與毛帝潤之相肩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>如此偉大<br />\n卻不搞個人崇拜 務實做事<br />\n真是謙虛至極、深藏若虛 啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n國家得此帝 實在是百姓之福 萬民之福 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於中美大戰中<br />\n本可救天下黎民於水深火熱 一統江山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong>要不是港區妖婦月娥作亂 誤了時機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><br />\n他早就可以反攻美帝 一統天下 早日登基<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成為平定全球的<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">習終帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">他媽的<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n我們必須要打倒妖婦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不能被那妖婦誤了大事<br />\n</strong></span>"},{"pid":"7e9d771ed719a8751c40e8f985e030725a149ee0","tid":1500631,"uid":213969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:39:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">真是佩服他呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"f778cd8c60bfa33c7e9e4fbc9a964d8ef02659ed","tid":1500631,"uid":174049,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:40:43.000Z","msg":"好撚偉大呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74b5923a8bf681a21e703eb1089de569ba86ac6d","tid":1500631,"uid":213969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:42:10.000Z","msg":"妖婦<br />\n習帝早已和你割蓆<br />\n速速投降<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c386ef63a9a779d02a16a445203583ffc743c6bf","tid":1500631,"uid":838,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T05:42:26.000Z","msg":"功成不必在我"},{"pid":"7e3cf41c56058ea40e6d7ed207aee7e5f2339aa8","tid":1500631,"uid":181156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"諡號：聖文神武開元終焉天皇大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e4d6e88798ca72414eb52efa68a67c7b07cb48","tid":1500631,"uid":213969,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"7e3cf41c56058ea40e6d7ed207aee7e5f2339aa8","tid":1500631,"uid":181156,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:02:12.000Z","msg":"諡號：聖文神武開元終焉天皇大帝<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:04:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />習則天"},{"pid":"bf5b8782e2b68f5c6d9cd37091da970789729768","tid":1500631,"uid":282910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:17:40.000Z","msg":"國書"},{"pid":"2f8124a6da1889448dcd3d15593322a3a5b56e59","tid":1500631,"uid":101481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T06:26:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/4897249878851